"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1642269326,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"ywucIyPFTQneS--dG1o1ean4NMDOrZkrQ6YskEAgT6Q\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x321c96b6B393ac40702D5e67CE2246fb805e3225\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"F-czF4JSVQwRzY6AvCKDVfDbkIJhjJeUpJYUYi71B5Q\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"rQaxwfLHbs4SSr6fvvfi2IIaXppiYY-G397k69VkRzg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"snLRJz6KUGl9Jd0no36qgmDz3Wk5XOC0GDBooxlQRVF8FBAvhX3uEcvc01lvRVtse4JMS2SzVEi4VgcSsJpEGw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x0d17d202b258f7fc340600b2c7d66e3ef6313493ed188680eea9c9012d6e36273567d753c9994281921da4dc74956d8e730c37f7c8aff1bb16259b648d6774801c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"F-czF4JSVQwRzY6AvCKDVfDbkIJhjJeUpJYUYi71B5Q\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"rQaxwfLHbs4SSr6fvvfi2IIaXppiYY-G397k69VkRzg\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi